### 3. Backend - 13 Mongoose Models

All models enforce NOT NULL and UNIQUE constraints as per the Data Dictionary.

#### [NEW] [Admin.js](file:///c:/Users/kusha/OneDrive/Pictures/Desktop/minor/backend/models/Admin.js)

| Field | Type | Constraints |
|-------|------|-------------|
| admin_id | ObjectId | Primary Key |
| name | String | Required |
| email | String | Required, Unique |
| password | String | Required (bcrypt hashed) |
| phone | String | Regex: 10-15 digits |
| role | String | Enum: ['super_admin', 'admin'] |

#### [NEW] [Student.js](file:///c:/Users/kusha/OneDrive/Pictures/Desktop/minor/backend/models/Student.js)

| Field | Type | Constraints |
|-------|------|-------------|
| student_id | ObjectId | Primary Key |
| enrollment_no | String | Required, Unique |
| name | String | Required |
| email | String | Required, Unique |
| password | String | Required (bcrypt hashed) |
| phone | String | Regex: 10-15 digits |
| department_id | ObjectId | Ref: Department |
| semester | Number | 1-8 |

#### [NEW] [Faculty.js](file:///c:/Users/kusha/OneDrive/Pictures/Desktop/minor/backend/models/Faculty.js)

| Field | Type | Constraints |
|-------|------|-------------|
| faculty_id | ObjectId | Primary Key |
| employee_id | String | Required, Unique |
| name | String | Required |
| email | String | Required, Unique |
| password | String | Required (bcrypt hashed) |
| phone | String | Regex: 10-15 digits |
| department_id | ObjectId | Ref: Department |
| designation | String | Required |

