### 4. Backend - Core Services

#### [NEW] [qrService.js](file:///c:/Users/kusha/OneDrive/Pictures/Desktop/minor/backend/services/qrService.js)

Generates unique QR codes for each registration using the `qrcode` npm package. Each QR encodes the `registration_id` for faculty scanning.

#### [NEW] [pdfService.js](file:///c:/Users/kusha/OneDrive/Pictures/Desktop/minor/backend/services/pdfService.js)

Auto-generates participation/winner certificates using `pdfkit`:
- Student name and enrollment number
- Event name and date
- Position (if winner)
- CDGI logo and signature lines

#### [NEW] [rankingService.js](file:///c:/Users/kusha/OneDrive/Pictures/Desktop/minor/backend/services/rankingService.js)

Calculates ranks from scores and auto-assigns prizes:
```javascript
// Algorithm: Sort by score DESC в†’ Assign ranks в†’ Map prizes
```

#### [NEW] [socketService.js](file:///c:/Users/kusha/OneDrive/Pictures/Desktop/minor/backend/services/socketService.js)

Socket.io integration for real-time:
- Event announcements
- Result publishing
- Payment confirmations

