### 5. Backend - Authentication & Security

#### [NEW] [auth.js](file:///c:/Users/kusha/OneDrive/Pictures/Desktop/minor/backend/middleware/auth.js)

JWT verification middleware with token refresh support.

#### [NEW] [roleGuard.js](file:///c:/Users/kusha/OneDrive/Pictures/Desktop/minor/backend/middleware/roleGuard.js)

Role-based access control:
- `requireAdmin()` - Admin-only routes
- `requireFaculty()` - Faculty + Admin
- `requireStudent()` - Student-only routes

#### [NEW] [sanitize.js](file:///c:/Users/kusha/OneDrive/Pictures/Desktop/minor/backend/middleware/sanitize.js)

NoSQL injection protection using `express-mongo-sanitize`.

---

### 6. Backend - API Routes

| Route Group | Base Path | Protected | Purpose |
|-------------|-----------|-----------|---------|
| Auth | `/api/auth` | No | Login, Register, Logout |
| Admin | `/api/admin` | Admin | User management, Reports |
| Student | `/api/students` | Student | Profile, Registrations |
| Faculty | `/api/faculty` | Faculty | QR scan, Results |
| Events | `/api/events` | Mixed | CRUD, Browse |
| Registration | `/api/registrations` | Student | Register algorithm |
| Payments | `/api/payments` | Student | Process, Status |
| Results | `/api/results` | Faculty | Score entry, Rankings |
| Notifications | `/api/notifications` | All | Real-time updates |

