### 8. Frontend - Key Components

#### [NEW] [EventRegistration.jsx](file:///c:/Users/kusha/OneDrive/Pictures/Desktop/minor/frontend/src/components/student/EventRegistration.jsx)

Core registration component implementing the Event Registration Algorithm:

```mermaid
flowchart TD
    A[Student clicks Register] --> B{Check Deadline}
    B -- Passed --> Z[Show Error]
    B -- Valid --> C{Check Availability}
    C -- Full --> Z
    C -- Available --> D{Already Registered?}
    D -- Yes --> Z
    D -- No --> E[Create Registration]
    E --> F[Generate QR Code]
    F --> G{Paid Event?}
    G -- Yes --> H[Create Pending Payment]
    G -- No --> I[Confirm Registration]
    H --> J[Show Payment Modal]
    I --> K[Show QR Code]
    J --> L[Process Payment]
    L --> M{Payment Success?}
    M -- Yes --> I
    M -- No --> N[Retry/Cancel]
```

#### [NEW] [QRDisplay.jsx](file:///c:/Users/kusha/OneDrive/Pictures/Desktop/minor/frontend/src/components/student/QRDisplay.jsx)

Displays student's QR code for event entry with download option.

#### [NEW] [QRScanner.jsx](file:///c:/Users/kusha/OneDrive/Pictures/Desktop/minor/frontend/src/components/faculty/QRScanner.jsx)

Camera-based QR scanner for faculty using `react-qr-reader`.

#### [NEW] [AdminDashboard.jsx](file:///c:/Users/kusha/OneDrive/Pictures/Desktop/minor/frontend/src/pages/AdminDashboard.jsx)

Analytics dashboard featuring:
- Registration statistics cards
- Payment revenue charts (Recharts)
- Event category filters (Technical/Cultural/Sports)
- Recent activity feed

#### [NEW] [StudentDashboard.jsx](file:///c:/Users/kusha/OneDrive/Pictures/Desktop/minor/frontend/src/pages/StudentDashboard.jsx)

Interactive dashboard with:
- Upcoming events browser with filters
